import Mathlib

lemma abs_sinh_le_exp_half (z : ℂ) : abs (Complex.sinh z) ≤ (1 / 2) * Real.exp (abs z) := by sorry

lemma abs_cosh_le_exp_half (z : ℂ) : abs (Complex.cosh z) ≤ (1 / 2) * Real.exp (abs z) := by sorry
